title: Dallas man arrested in 1984 killing of aspiring model - Yahoo News
content: Dallas man arrested in 1984 killing of aspiring model  Yahoo NewsView Full Coverage on Google News
description: Investigators arrested a 60-year-old Dallas man on a capital murder charge in the 1984 killing of a 21-year-old woman after linking him to the crime through genealogical databases, prosecutors said Friday.  Edward Morgan was arrested in the killing of Mary Jane Thompson, who was also sexually assaulted, the Dallas County district attorney's office said.  Morgan was being held Friday at the Dallas County jail.
